ובפרט מתכנס.
 נתמקד ב
\begin_inset Formula $x\ne x_{0}$
\end_inset

, ונסמן 
\begin_inset Formula $\forall k\in\mathbb{N}\,b_{k}=a_{k}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{k}$
\end_inset

.
 אזי מתקיים:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sqrt[k]{\left|b_{k}\right|} & =\sqrt[k]{\left|a_{k}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{k}\right|}=\sqrt[k]{\left|a_{k}\right|}\cdot\sqrt[k]{\left|x-x_{0}\right|^{k}}=\sqrt[k]{\left|a_{k}\right|}\cdot\left|x-x_{0}\right|\iff\\
\iff & \underset{k\rightarrow\infty}{\limsup}\sqrt[k]{\left|b_{k}\right|}=\underset{k\rightarrow\infty}{\limsup}\sqrt[k]{\left|a_{k}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{k}\right|}=\left|x-x_{0}\right|\underset{k\rightarrow\infty}{\limsup}\sqrt[k]{\left|a_{k}\right|}=L\left|x-x_{0}\right|
\end{align*}

\end_inset

לכן מתקיים: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
\begin_inset Formula $L=0$
\end_inset

 אזי 
\begin_inset Formula $L\left|x-x_{0}\right|=0$
\end_inset

