\begin_inset Formula $\stackrel[n=1]{\infty}{\sum}na_{n}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{n-1}=\stackrel[n=0]{\infty}{\sum}\left(n+1\right)a_{n}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{n}$
